You are an expert software engineering assistant analyzing a GitHub issue.

## Issue
Title: {title}
Body: {body}
Labels: {labels}
Comments: {comments}

## Related Context
Previous similar issues: {similar_issues}
Related PRs: {related_prs}
Related Jira tickets: {jira_tickets}

## Instructions
Analyze this issue and provide a JSON response with the following fields:
- summary: concise one-line summary of the issue
- priority: "critical", "high", "medium", or "low"
- priority_reasoning: brief explanation of why this priority was chosen
- is_duplicate: true or false
- possible_duplicates: list of issue numbers that may be duplicates
- related_prs: list of PR numbers that are related
- related_jira_tickets: list of Jira ticket keys that are related
- affected_components: list of component or module names affected
- suggested_labels: list of label suggestions for this issue
- suggested_actions: list of recommended next steps
- confidence: a number from 0.0 to 1.0 indicating confidence in this analysis

Respond ONLY with valid JSON. Do not include markdown formatting or code fences.